{"tid":2434830,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想知大家點同另一半講結婚呢個決定","createTime":"2021-03-05T19:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T03:59:36.000Z","uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d408a595d9a10a83f11aca8750c0484bab06d08","tid":2434830,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:05:37.000Z","msg":"如果女士開聲，啲男人又話俾壓力佢，又話趕住搵人埋單<br />\n但男人又好似好少會提結婚嘅野。如果大家拍咗一段時間感情好穩定，通常會係女士提出定男士呢？"},{"pid":"292e6f0335d2919c256c7cdfcc3cee349efc5896","tid":2434830,"uid":33222,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有一樣嘢叫做求婚"},{"pid":"917a16258ab3cb99e04facc77ead272437eff169","tid":2434830,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"拍拖一星期左右老公已經問我係咪以結婚為目標"},{"pid":"109114316d65dfc70ecda46d8f8521903dab8efd","tid":2434830,"uid":9392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:08:25.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair準備婚手 開心～"},{"pid":"4a1787547146218b7e355afd263aba6f2e328850","tid":2434830,"uid":77959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"292e6f0335d2919c256c7cdfcc3cee349efc5896","tid":2434830,"uid":33222,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有一樣嘢叫做求婚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"求婚前唔會探下口風/傾下有無plan嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到求婚果下fail點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a0fbc19ff1923156bb45ee247b61cf12176915","tid":2434830,"uid":33222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a1787547146218b7e355afd263aba6f2e328850","tid":2434830,"uid":77959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"292e6f0335d2919c256c7cdfcc3cee349efc5896","tid":2434830,"uid":33222,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有一樣嘢叫做求婚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"求婚前唔會探下口風/傾下有無plan嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到求婚果下fail點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"去到嗰個階段大家心照啦<br />\n傾計都會傾下未來架"},{"pid":"138831013fbf3780ee0d16c082af2f174f163467","tid":2434830,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:14:39.000Z","msg":"想一齊移民所以結婚"},{"pid":"1b2d57d42fc72feb4a56366f9966cdd797fbd835","tid":2434830,"uid":41238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"292e6f0335d2919c256c7cdfcc3cee349efc5896","tid":2434830,"uid":33222,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有一樣嘢叫做求婚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁你都會討論下㗎嘛，例如結婚之後住邊租屋定買樓，諗住拍幾多年結婚<br />\n<br />\n唔會冇啦啦乜都冇傾過你就去求婚"},{"pid":"a323cce9017d908fb47fd2819c13fc91cb760cae","tid":2434830,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"917a16258ab3cb99e04facc77ead272437eff169","tid":2434830,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"拍拖一星期左右老公已經問我係咪以結婚為目標"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"我都係，但點樣講真係想計畫下結婚？"},{"pid":"eee6e469b52695de540d3bdd15346e30bf260bf3","tid":2434830,"uid":44277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a323cce9017d908fb47fd2819c13fc91cb760cae","tid":2434830,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"917a16258ab3cb99e04facc77ead272437eff169","tid":2434830,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"拍拖一星期左右老公已經問我係咪以結婚為目標"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"我都係，但點樣講真係想計畫下結婚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:27:00.000Z","msg":"冇特別講㗎喎<br />\n跟住拍拖嗰陣咪又會傾下覺得收入幾多先生仔呀<br />\n結婚之後住邊呀租定買之類<br />\n佢問我想幾歲前結，我話30歲前結咁囉<br />\n嗰陣一齊一兩年左右我就去咗佢屋企同居<br />\n跟住就到咁上下時間就話搬出去住（嗰陣我29歲）<br />\n之後咪一齊book日子結婚"},{"pid":"82e7c00d6d3dd9541987856948b79b4aff9ab773","tid":2434830,"uid":280264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得最好拍拖初期已經講定<br />\n結唔結婚 生唔生仔<br />\n好過之後日子耐左 發現呢方面唔夾<br />\n仲傷"},{"pid":"bf3a203e09b09f6fc1c66265e5b0d2c568fc7ac3","tid":2434830,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"計劃條撚咩<br />\n份工又唔穩定<br />\n同住要兩三年先一齊<br />\n時唔時又要我結婚 痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n樣樣都係錢 唔係一個yes no問題咁簡單<br />\n但女人多數唔撚會理e d問題"},{"pid":"3fea7f5a4dafc57271d629499a52c8d1fc47b0b7","tid":2434830,"uid":75597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩一齊就知大家會一直落去（即係認定啦）<br />\n一齊兩個月佢求婚<br />\n然後咪開始plan下<br />\n簡單搞<br />\n婚前三個月去註冊處預約<br />\n就係咁"},{"pid":"4e15d994b7d3d68f411c876b736bdad726829d18","tid":2434830,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ae39becb112bef2518c94809147b78ea568b90","tid":2434830,"uid":75597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e15d994b7d3d68f411c876b736bdad726829d18","tid":2434830,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2660f2f4cbd4f5ec3e4381d19b6270e9751e42","tid":2434830,"uid":181527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ae39becb112bef2518c94809147b78ea568b90","tid":2434830,"uid":75597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e15d994b7d3d68f411c876b736bdad726829d18","tid":2434830,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score"